The Duke and Duchess of Sussex visited the UK last week as they joined the nation in celebrating the Queen’s Platinum Jubilee. A report in The Sun claims that, during their return, Harry, 37, and Meghan, 40, spent a quarter of an hour with the monarch, 96. The source told the Sun: “It was a quick in and out job. It was all quite formal.” Buckingham Palace declined a request for comment. READ BELOW FOR MORE UPDATES...